[14.86275, "o", "\r\n"]
[14.869279, "o", "\u001b[H\u001b[2J\u001b[3J\r\n━━━ 2 · Three commands (slash commands after install) ━━━\r\n\r\n"]
[16.883613, "o", "$ npx aicrew --help | sed -n \"/AFTER INSTALL/,+12p\"\r\n"]
[17.123861, "o", "AFTER INSTALL\r\n"]
[17.124348, "o", "  Claude Code — daily slash commands:\r\n"]
[17.124509, "o", "    /dev             — full development pipeline (bug fix, feature, refactor)\r\n    /fix             — fast bug fix (3 questions, no ceremony)\r\n    /quick           — Scout → Act (graph-first, Karpathy guardrails)\r\n"]
[17.124827, "o", "    /conclude        — save session learnings to memory\r\n"]
[17.125072, "o", "    /brainstorm  /handoff  /session  /lean   (/normal = /lean off)\r\n    Maintenance (rare): /update-skills  /harness-audit  /benchmark\r\n    Setup actions (install/update/status/agent-kit/cursor-plugin) are CLI commands above.\r\n"]
[17.125412, "o", "\r\n"]
[17.125591, "o", "  Codex — skill names:\r\n    aicrew-dev, aicrew-fix, aicrew-quick, aicrew-conclude, aicrew-harness-audit\r\n    aicrew-update-skills, brainstorm, lean\r\n"]
[22.137448, "o", "\r\n$ npx aicrew --help | sed -n \"/Maintenance/,+3p\"\r\n"]
[22.416644, "o", "    Maintenance (rare): /update-skills  /harness-audit  /benchmark\r\n    Setup actions (install/update/status/agent-kit/cursor-plugin) are CLI commands above.\r\n\r\n  Codex — skill names:\r\n"]
[27.433872, "o", "\r\n"]
[27.434463, "o", "\u001b[H\u001b[2J\u001b[3J"]
[27.434893, "o", "\r\n"]
[27.435402, "o", "━━━ 3 · Pipeline depth — phase gates ━━━\r\n\r\n"]
[29.438965, "o", "$ cat docs/demo-script.txt\r\n"]
[29.439234, "o", "══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\r\n"]
[29.595205, "o", "  aicrew pipelines — phase gates at a glance\r\n"]
[29.750547, "o", "══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\r\n"]
[29.904974, "o", "\r\n"]
[30.060293, "o", "/dev — 9 phases (features, refactors, multi-system work)\r\n"]
[30.215289, "o", "  0 Intake       → acceptance criteria + pipeline confirmed\r\n"]
[30.369356, "o", "  1 Research     → Scout pass; root cause OR key files classified\r\n"]
[30.524604, "o", "  2 Brainstorm   → 3 alternatives; user picks approach\r\n"]
[30.679626, "o", "  3 Design       → architect spec confirmed — no code yet\r\n"]
[30.837553, "o", "  4 Implement    → TDD strict: RED → GREEN → REFACTOR\r\n"]
[30.997923, "o", "  5 Tests        → test engineer PASS; new code coverage ≥ 80%\r\n"]
[31.14858, "o", "  6 Security     → security-reviewer PASS on changed files only\r\n"]
[31.302637, "o", "  7 Audit        → project /audit PASS (if included at intake)\r\n"]
[31.464037, "o", "  8 Cloud/Infra  → auto on schema, deps, deploy changes\r\n"]
[31.625652, "o", "  9 Conclude     → memory saved, diff --stat, commit msg ready\r\n"]
[31.795486, "o", "\r\n"]
[31.968645, "o", "/fix — 5 phases (known bugs — fast path, fixed pipeline)\r\n"]
[32.134567, "o", "  1 Bug Analysis → confirmed root cause BEFORE any code\r\n"]
[32.296651, "o", "  2 Implement    → failing repro test → fix → suite green\r\n"]
[32.454684, "o", "  3 Tests        → test engineer PASS; coverage ≥ 80%\r\n"]
[32.613609, "o", "  4 Security     → security-reviewer PASS on changed files\r\n"]
[32.772943, "o", "  5 Conclude     → summary, diff --stat, commit message ready\r\n"]
[32.930713, "o", "\r\n"]
[33.088011, "o", "/quick — Scout → Act (small scoped tasks)\r\n"]
[33.245927, "o", "  Scout → graph-first discovery (haiku/mini) → SCOUT: schema block\r\n"]
[33.402261, "o", "  Act   → surgical change with Scout context only (sonnet/opus)\r\n"]
[33.558064, "o", "  Escalate to /fix for bugs; to /dev for design spec or infra.\r\n"]
[33.713248, "o", "\r\n"]
[33.870914, "o", "Token economics (illustrative discovery cost):\r\n"]
[34.02802, "o", "  repo-wide grep scan     ~80,000 tokens\r\n"]
[34.185165, "o", "  graph MCP query (Scout) ~500 tokens  (~99% savings)\r\n"]
[34.341779, "o", "  → aicrew benchmark below — repo-specific estimates\r\n"]
[39.503234, "o", "\r\n"]
[39.504928, "o", "\u001b[H\u001b[2J\u001b[3J"]
[39.505423, "o", "\r\n━━━ 4 · Token savings — real benchmark ━━━\r\n\r\n"]
[41.513664, "o", "$ aicrew benchmark\r\n"]
[41.853429, "o", "\r\naicrew benchmark — scanning /home/abhi/Workspace/aicrew ...\r\n\r\n"]
[41.878778, "o", "Files scanned  : 118\r\nBaseline est.  : ~385.0K tokens\r\n"]
[41.879004, "o", "With aicrew    : ~23.0K tokens\r\nSaved          : ~362.0K tokens (94%)\r\n"]
[41.879061, "o", "\r\nBy feature:\r\n  /quick Scout → Act                   79.3K saved  (99%)\r\n"]
[41.879621, "o", "  /lean slice reads                     6.1K saved  (68%)\r\n"]
[41.880455, "o", "  graph MCP (codebase-memory-mcp)     238.5K saved  (99%)\r\n"]
[41.880586, "o", "  /handoff + .ai/state                 14.7K saved  (98%)\r\n"]
[41.880662, "o", "  /dev phase compaction                21.6K saved  (60%)\r\n  caveman/terse output                  1.8K saved  (35%)\r\n"]
[41.881188, "o", "\r\nTip: add --report to write a full markdown report to .ai/reports/\r\n"]
[47.900776, "o", "\r\n"]
[47.902406, "o", "\u001b[H\u001b[2J\u001b[3J"]
[47.902877, "o", "\r\n━━━ 5 · Learn more ━━━\r\n\r\n"]
[49.909093, "o", "  Full reference → docs/pipeline-overview.md\r\n  Install now      → npx aicrew install\r\n"]
